{"tid":2369370,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"實體漫畫","createTime":"2021-01-17T05:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T15:47:42.000Z","uid":374001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd7c03751b42e39ddbba5be17e0b7c8a7893566","tid":2369370,"uid":374001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"呢排開始睇完一套漫畫之後會去買返黎儲，或者未睇但評價好嘅都會買返黎睇。 雖然有人話而家仲買漫畫好浪費錢，但我始終覺得漫畫係要揸係手睇最好，而且儲漫畫其實同儲figures一樣，一排排放係度好治癒。 唔知有冇人同我一樣，仲會買同收藏漫畫？"},{"pid":"28ef1ea2567d4d902a1f2f5c8f456986e2345419","tid":2369370,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"屌可惜香港人唔係個個好似你咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個寧願畀漫畫人偷個資都買實體書，係死都唔買"},{"pid":"81909fa10063460c0caac95240e7c8603b3c682b","tid":2369370,"uid":374001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28ef1ea2567d4d902a1f2f5c8f456986e2345419","tid":2369370,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"屌可惜香港人唔係個個好似你咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個寧願畀漫畫人偷個資都買實體書，係死都唔買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"無辦法，畢竟而家大多數漫畫上網可以免費睇，一定少咗好多人會keep住買，再加上香港嘅家居地理限制...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我平時就算唔買，剩係行漫畫店已經覺得好正，享受個種氛圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae48c0703dd42a23de4b454ab1399578b2f52385","tid":2369370,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:27:38.000Z","msg":"買電子版多<br />\n好鐘意先會買實體<br />\n屋企無位放"},{"pid":"3122373b34dc91eac4c705ac13a55a3b3e11f73d","tid":2369370,"uid":145446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"真係好鐘意會買嚟儲，可惜基本上得返信和有得賣"},{"pid":"e3d9fc6a1595dc5bc50ca19239254befd7f93962","tid":2369370,"uid":374001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3122373b34d